## [{{ version }}]
### Added
- ci: Add workflow rules to prevent duplicate push/MR pipelines
- ci: Add artifacts templates
- ubuntu: Add bash-completion

### Changed
- ubuntu: Update shell library to 2.0.0 in ubuntu image
